data.name: Green Apple and Spinach Juice
data.quickTastyDescription: A refreshing and nutritious juice packed with vitamins and minerals, perfect for a quick energy boost.
detailedCookingInstructions: Wash the green apples thoroughly and chop them into quarters, removing the seeds.
Rinse the fresh spinach under cold water to remove any dirt or grit.
In a blender, combine the chopped green apples, fresh spinach, lemon juice, and water.
Blend on high speed until smooth and well combined.
If desired, add honey for sweetness and blend again.
Strain the mixture through a fine sieve or cheesecloth into a glass if you prefer a smoother juice, or enjoy it as is with the pulp.
Serve immediately over ice, if desired.
data.modifiersForBase: Add lemon juice and honey for flavor
